Health Districts 1-1, 1-2, 2-0, 3-1, 3-2, 3-4, 4-0, and 5-2; M Vello,
MPH, Georgia Div of Public Health; North Carolina Amateur Softball
Assoc; Virology Section, North Carolina State Laboratory for Public
Health; M Buchanan, MD, Knox County Health Dept; M Zylstra,
Chattanooga-Hamilton County Health Dept; McLean County Health Dept; C
